# 從頭再嚟
(pos:動詞)
<explanation>
yue:由頭部開始，然後再回來（量詞：個）
eng:come back from the beginning
<eg>
yue:佢好會做，佢就係由頭再嚟。 (ge3 ziu1 ziu1 ziu1 ziu1 ziu1 ziu1 ziu1 ziu1.)
eng:He is good at it, he just comes back from the beginning.

<eg>
yue:佢好會做，佢就係由頭再嚟。 (ge3 ziu1 ziu1 ziu1 ziu1 ziu1 ziu1 ziu1 ziu1.)
eng:He is good at it, he just comes back from the beginning. [end of text]


